                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#iiv(erso) #iii r(ecto)"/>": Spiritual Rewards (fruits) for reciting the Lord’s Prayer and the <title type="complete" ref="LIT2000Mazmur"/>
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez"/>በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ንዑ፡ ስምዑኒ፡ ወእንግርክሙ፡ ዘወሀበክሙ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ መፍቀሬ፡ ሰብእ፡ ለውሉደ፡ አዳም፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ከመዝ፡ ይከውን፡ ፍሬሁ፡ ለአቡነ፡ ዘበሰማያት፡ ዘይጼሊ፡ በቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡</foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
